sentences: Andrew Benton Hawkins (born April 28, 1965) is a composer, record producer and guitarist from Missouri as well as a founding member of the band Blind Idiot God.
Andrew Benton Hawkins was born on April 28, 1965 and grew up in St. Louis, Missouri.

sentences: While still a teenager, he formed Blind Idiot God with Ted Epstein and Gabriel Katz in 1982.

sentences: In 1987, the band released their debut album, the eponymously titled Blind Idiot God, to great acclaim in the underground musical community.
